                           <q xml:lang="en">Fols. 128va-128vb (bottom): Listen to our Lord, all you churches, for He is the one who glorified the ˀOrit and the Prophets in the Gospel of the Kingdom saying, Krǝstos son of David, “Amen…”</q>
